products.description: FLEECE TO FEEL GOOD ABOUT - Hanes EcoSmart midweight sweatshirt is made with cotton sourced from American farms.     STAY WARM - Designed with a kid-safe, cord-free hood to help block out wind and chill.     ZIP FRONT - Classic full-zip styling for easy on-and-off.     DESIGN DETAILS - Features stretch ribbed cuffs and hem for a cozy fit.     TAG FREE - No need to worry about annoying tags bunching up, thanks to our Tagless interior.     COLD WATER WASH - Hanes recommends machine washing this jacket in cold water to reduce energy usage.
